class_description:
This class represents the ASN.1 encoding of a public key,
 encoded according to the ASN.1 type SubjectPublicKeyInfo.
 The SubjectPublicKeyInfo syntax is defined in the X.509
 standard as follows:

params.param_description:
the key, which is assumed to be
 encoded according to the X.509 standard. The contents of the
 array are copied to protect against subsequent modification.

Methods.method_description: Creates a new X509EncodedKeySpec with the given encoded key.

return_description:
the X.509 encoding of the key. Returns a new array
 each time this method is called.

Methods.method_description: Returns the key bytes, encoded according to the X.509 standard.

Returns the name of the encoding format associated with this
 key specification.
